subject: College Athletics
Wrestling
lead_paragraph: Cornell’s Kyle Dake, a 21-year-old senior who is the top-ranked wrestler at 165 pounds, defeated No. 13 Zach Toal of Missouri and No. 3 Tyler Caldwell of Oklahoma State and was named the outstanding wrestler at Grapple at the Garden,
